<p>The <code>BreadcrumbListItem</code> wraps one rung of the trail.
  Pass <code>current: true</code> for the item representing the
  current page — the macro sets <code>aria-current="page"</code> so
  screen readers announce it correctly.</p>

<p>See the <a href="/components/breadcrumb-nav/">BreadcrumbNav demo</a>
  for usage.</p>
